<div id="pf5" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="5"><div class="pc pc5 w0 h0"><div class="t m61 x26 h12 y68 ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why Do </div><div class="t m62 x26 h12 y69 ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christians Give </div><div class="t m63 x26 h12 y6a ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Offerings? </div><div class="t m64 x26 h13 y6b ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">111 To ensure God&apos;s continued protection? </div><div class="t m65 x26 h13 y6c ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">111 Because everyone is expected to give? </div><div class="t m42 x27 h14 y6d ff6 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">‚ùë </div><div class="t m66 x28 h13 y6e ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To appease one&apos;s conscience? </div><div class="t m67 x29 h15 y6f ff4 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7 </div><div class="t m68 x29 h13 y70 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t m69 x2a h13 y71 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">express love and </div><div class="t m6a x2b h13 y72 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ratitude to God? </div><div class="t m6b x29 h15 y73 ff4 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">r </div><div class="t m68 x29 h13 y74 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t m6c x2a h13 y75 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hasten the work </div><div class="t m6d x10 h13 y76 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of God in the earth? </div><div class="t m6e x27 h16 y77 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No Other Way </div><div class="t m6f x2c h17 y78 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The Lord does not need our </div><div class="t m70 x2d h17 y79 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">offerings. We cannot enrich Him by </div><div class="t m71 x2d h17 y7a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our gifts. Says the psalmist, &quot;All </div><div class="t m72 x2d h17 y7b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thins come of thee, and of thine </div><div class="t m73 x2d h17 y7c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">owave we given thee.&quot; </div><div class="t m2 x4 h17 y7c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Yet God </div><div class="t m74 x2d h17 y7d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">permits us to show our appreciation </div><div class="t m75 x2d h17 y7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of his mercies by self-sactific </div><div class="t m76 x2d h17 y7f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">efforts to extend the same to others. </div><div class="t m77 x2d h17 y80 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This is the only way in which it is </div><div class="t m78 x2d h17 y81 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">possible for us to manifest our </div><div class="t m4 x27 h17 y82 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gratitude and love to God. He </div><div class="t m79 x2d h17 y83 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has provided no other way&quot; </div><div class="t m7a x2e h18 y84 ff3 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Review and Herald, </div><div class="t m7b x5 h18 y85 ff2 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dec. 6. 1887). </div><div class="t m7c x1a h19 y86 ff7 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Express your gratitude this quarter </div><div class="t m7d x1d h19 y87 ff7 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through systematic planned giving. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
